3D Parametric Solid Model Drawing
Am 27.11.2013 verffentlicht
Abonnieren 27 Tsd.
This video displays a setting up of 61 chain links and 2 sprockets along a defined paths in Assembly modelling environment of Autodesk Inventor . [We invite everyone to visit our blog at following link http://bit.ly/3D_Parametric_Solid_Mod...] First of all some base sketching afterward some advance pattern, adaptive features and assembly mates are to be applied to set up an animation matching the real world scenario Later the whole mechanism consisting of required mates are driven by using Inventor Studio functionality of the software. .............................................................................................. Dear viewers an advance version of this video tutorial showing the animation of 70 Chain Links along with 3 Sprockets can be seen on the following link https://youtu.be/UQo94WZqz7U . You may get the file required to complete this tutorial by visiting our content list of the videos on the following link --- http://niveshandnisheeth.blogspot.com... ................................................................................... Our motive to upload this video is to show our work ability/experience, so as to get job in the appropriate field.
